---

<footer class="text-white py-8" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #111111, #1c1c1e, #004d40);">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
        <img src="/assets/Group 137.svg" alt="GDG Logo Logo" width="300" height="300" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm text-center md:text-left">
        Acompanhe nossos eventos, projetos e novidades em tempo real Junte-se à conversa e
        compartilhe experiências com outros desenvolvedores apaixonados por tecnologia
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center border-t border-gray-800 pt-6 pb-4">
      <nav class="flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-0">
        <a
          href="/sobre"
          class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          Sobre Nós
        </a>
        <a
          href="/recursos"
          class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          Recursos
        </a>
        <a
          href="/planos"
          class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          Planos
        </a>
        <a href="/faq" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm">
          FAQ
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contacto"
          class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          Contacto
        </a>
      </nav>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://www.facebook.com/gdgportugal"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
          aria-label="Facebook"
        >
          f
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://twitter.com/gdgportugal"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
          aria-label="Twitter"
        >
          𝕏
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/gdg-portugal"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
          aria-label="LinkedIn"
        >
          in
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/gdgportugal"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
          aria-label="Instagram"
        >
          📷
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-800 pt-4 text-gray-500 text-xs flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
      <p>©2024 GDG Portugal. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
      <div class="mt-2 md:mt-0">
        <span class="text-gray-500">gdgportugal@gmail.com</span>
        <span class="mx-2">|</span>
        <span class="text-gray-500">+351 910 000 000</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
